{{Infobox book <!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject_Novels or Wikipedia:WikiProject_Books --> | name = Rabbit Makes a Monkey of Lion | image = Rabbit Makes a Monkey of Lion.jpg | image_size = 200 | caption = | author = [[Verna Aardema]] | illustrator = [[Jerry Pinkney]] | country = [[United States]] | language = English | genre = Children's [[picture book]], | published = 1989 ([[Dial Press]]) | media_type = Print ([[hardback]]) | pages = 28 (unpaginated) | isbn = 9780803702981 | oclc = 13581887 }}
'''''Rabbit Makes a Monkey of Lion: A Swahili Tale''''' is a 1989 children's picture book by [[Verna Aardema]] and illustrated by [[Jerry Pinkney]]. It is an adaption of a [[Swahili people|Swahili]] [[Oral tradition|folktale]] and is about Rabbit [[Trickster|tricking]] Lion over a [[calabash tree]].
==Reception== ''[[Publishers Weekly]]'' reviewed ''Rabbit Makes a Monkey of Lion'' writing "Aardema offers up a sound piece of storytelling, admirably reflected in Pinkney's full-color watercolor and pencil illustrations; he composes a lush jungle setting for the folksy antics, and brings drama to the text with his depictions of the various escapes from the hapless Lion."<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.publishersweekly.com/978-0-8037-0297-4 |title=Rabbit Makes a Monkey of Lion |date=February 27, 1989 |website=Publishers Weekly |publisher=PWxyz LLC|accessdate=December 27, 2016}}</ref> and the ''[[New York Times]]'' described Pinkney's illustrations as having "a velvety softness".<ref>{{cite news |last=Russo |first=Maria |date=September 17, 1989 |title=Children's Books: Bookshelf - Additional titles of interest|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/27/books/viva-frida-and-frida-diego.html?_r=0 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=December 27, 2016}}</ref>
''Rabbit Makes a Monkey of Lion'' has also been reviewed by the ''[[School Library Journal]]'',<ref>{{cite journal |date=June 1989 |title=Rabbit Makes a Monkey of Lion: a Swahili Tale (Book) |url=http://connection.ebscohost.com/c/book-reviews/10563857/rabbit-makes-monkey-lion-swahili-tale-book |journal=School Library Journal |publisher=Media Source Inc. |volume=35 |issue=10 |page=97 |accessdate=December 27, 2016}}</ref> and ''[[Booklist]]''.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.buffalolib.org/vufind/Record/551850/Reviews |title=Rabbit makes a monkey of lion : a Swahili tale |website=Buffalo and Erie County Public Library |accessdate=December 27, 2016}}</ref>
